headline: DAT introduces LaneMakers for DAT iQ Benchmark to help shippers find capacity for underserved lanes
summary: BEAVERTON, Ore., May 05, 2025--DAT Freight & Analytics introduced the integration of LaneMakers, a powerful tool for finding untapped truckload capacity, into its DAT iQ Benchmark™ freight analytics product. This enhancement gives shippers new capabilities to identify active carriers for underserved or underperforming lanes—without disrupting their benchmarking workflow.
